  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5587914/" class="title-link">如何赢得权力？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5587914"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunrise1984/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36335433-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sunrise1984/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">旭日方升</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-09-18"
      class="main-meta">2012-09-18 11:20:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5587914_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本书原名“The Hardball Handbook”，直译过来是“硬球手册”或“硬球指南”，如果不知道作者克里斯•马修斯是美国政治评论节目《硬球》的主持人，相信没几个人能明白“硬球手册”什么意思，更不会知道本书内容是关于哪方面的。所以，中国的策划编辑为其取了“权谋”这个名字...

